45:08.182 --> 45:10.118
congratulations, Luther.
Thank you.

45:10.184 --> 45:13.554
I thought it was
Jack Morrison's baby.
Luther had the winning time.

45:13.621 --> 45:18.192
Twenty-Two hours.
I could feel it in my Bones.
Where's my cash?

45:18.259 --> 45:21.295
Where's your ticket?
Huh? That's no problem.

45:21.362 --> 45:24.365
Don't worry.
I'll get it later.
Uh-Uh!

45:24.432 --> 45:28.002
No ticket, no money.
That's real cold, V.J.

45:28.069 --> 45:30.038
I'll be right back.

45:32.140 --> 45:35.209
Cathy, hi.
How 'bout a cigar?
Thank you.

45:35.276 --> 45:37.612
Want a light?
Oh, no.

45:37.679 --> 45:40.715
I need a refill.
Anybody else?
No.

45:40.782 --> 45:42.750
Me.
Okay.

45:50.358 --> 45:52.627
There you are.
I was getting worried.

45:52.694 --> 45:57.565
What's that awful smell?
I don't know.
Maybe my new Aftershave.

45:57.632 --> 45:59.667
[ sighs ]

45:59.734 --> 46:03.671
it smells like formaldehyde.
Well, I was in the morgue.

46:03.738 --> 46:06.374
Let me help you
wash it off.

46:06.441 --> 46:10.478
Shirley, let me explain.
I was just getting the latest
on the neilsen Autopsy.

46:10.545 --> 46:13.014
Hey, everybody,
here he is!

46:17.885 --> 46:20.288
It's gotta be here
someplace.

46:25.827 --> 46:28.696
Jack, Congratulations.
Thanks.

46:28.763 --> 46:31.165
How 'bout a cigar?
No, I don't smoke.

46:31.232 --> 46:34.302
Then get a drink.
Thanks.
It's quite a day.

46:34.369 --> 46:36.371
Yeah, I'll bet.

46:36.437 --> 46:39.974
How's Gene custodi doing?
You make any progress
with him?

46:40.041 --> 46:43.678
Jack, listen.
It's a party.

46:43.745 --> 46:45.713
What's wrong?

46:47.015 --> 46:50.918
Custodi killed himself
a couple of hours ago.

46:50.985 --> 46:54.622
What?
He left a note.

46:54.689 --> 46:57.091
What'd it say?

46:57.158 --> 47:01.129
"I hope the next world
is better than this."

47:03.664 --> 47:07.435
Please be here.
We talking about
big money here.

47:07.502 --> 47:10.772
Come on. Mega bucks.
We not talking about
just a few dollars.

47:10.838 --> 47:14.275
We talking about big cash.
Please be here. Come on.

47:14.342 --> 47:17.879
Here they are.
Dr. Auschlander.

47:17.945 --> 47:19.881
Dr. Westphall.
Steven, long time.

47:19.947 --> 47:22.717
Enjoying your externship?
Oh, yeah, the best.

47:22.784 --> 47:24.719
Everybody here's
really terrific.

47:24.786 --> 47:26.721
Any particular field
interest you yet?

47:26.788 --> 47:29.123
Cardiac surgery, of course.
Right, dad?

47:29.190 --> 47:31.192
That's right.
Should've guessed it.

47:31.259 --> 47:33.761
He is gonna make one hell
